132
00:11:50,934 --> 00:11:52,970
[外:BBDA644D17EFD3C020635EE3D90968A5]あっ？[外:38566B372F4C5A1AEAD4EFA20DECD079]

133
00:11:52,970 --> 00:11:56,006
・～

134
00:11:56,006 --> 00:11:58,675
[外:BBDA644D17EFD3C020635EE3D90968A5]らしくないよ｡ どうした？[外:38566B372F4C5A1AEAD4EFA20DECD079]

135
00:11:58,675 --> 00:12:02,679
